            <thetext>IS:

The NavigationPage consists a fix for a Android &lt; 4.1 bug, which causes problems on native input fields, when translate3d() is used on surrounding container.

SHOULD:
This bug has been fixed for 4.1 Jelly Bean, so this fix should not be activated on this version anymore. Translate3d() makes scrolling on iScroll much smoother,  instead of using &quot;position:relative&quot; moving method.

This needs an update of environment variable &quot;os.version&quot;, which should detect Android version, too. 
Depending on this detection, the &quot;androidQuirksMode&quot; can be disabled on iScroll.</thetext>
